SG ASIA Hydraulics does Installation, maintenance, modification, and fabrication of hydraulic winches, cranes, davits, cargo control systems, and other related hydraulic control equipment for the marine and oil &amp; gas industries.
Occasionally, our technical team goes onboard shipyard to service our customer's hydraulic equipment.
SG ASIA Hydraulics wants a competent individual willing to learn new things. He/she has to be able to work and communicate well with our team and be open to feedbacks.
